                            </p>
                            <p>
                                <strong>Approach:</strong>
                            </p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Developed synthetic data techniques to address historical biases in lending data</li>
                                <li>Implemented multiple fairness metrics to evaluate model performance</li>
                                <li>Created a transparent explanation system for both applicants and regulators</li>
                                <li>Established a human review process for edge cases and appeals</li>
